Standard and Poor's Corp said itraised to A-minus from BBB-plus Hechinger Co's 19.9 mln dlrs ofindustrial revenue bonds.    Yesterday, S and P upgraded to BBB-plus from BBB thecompany's 86 mln dlrs of convertible subordinated debentures of2009 and assigned a BBB-plus rating to Hechinger's planned 100mln dlr issue of convertible debt due 2012.    In its release yesterday, S and P cited what it termed anoutstanding record of sales and earnings growth by Hechinger. Reuter&#3;